nodes.text: Jai Quallo was a male Kaleesh Beast master living during the Galactic War. A member of the Dust Vipers gang operating on Tatooine, in 3630 BBY he was guarding the entrance to the gang's compound near Anchorhead when Eternal Alliance ambushed it, looking to reclaim stolen security codes of the Alliance base on Odessen. Jai Quallo and his beasts fought the intruders, but were overwhelmed and killed.
Jai Quallo appears in Star Wars: The Old Republic: Knights of the Eternal Throne as a boss during the "Done and Dusted" Uprising.
